==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Euchlorine
<hw>Eu*chlo"rine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>euchlorine</ets>. See <er>Euchloric</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A yellow or greenish yellow gas, first prepared by Davy, evolved
from potassium chlorate and hydrochloric acid. It is supposed to consist
of chlorine tetroxide with some free chlorine.</def></p>

